@startuml
title UC01 Credential owner registers a provider credential

actor "Credential owner" as Owner
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
participant "Upstream provider" as Provider
database "Firestore" as Firestore
collections "Cloud KMS" as KMS

Owner -> UI: Open the credential registration screen
UI --> Owner: Show the provider selector and API key form

Owner -> UI: Enter the provider and API key, then submit
UI -> API: Request credential creation
API -> Provider: Validate the API key
Provider --> API: Validation result

alt API key is valid
  API -> KMS: Request encryption-key operations
  KMS --> API: Return encryption material
  API -> Firestore: Store ciphertext and metadata
  Firestore --> API: Storage complete
  API --> UI: Registration succeeded
  UI --> Owner: Show success
else API key is invalid
  API --> UI: Registration failed
  UI --> Owner: Show an error
end
@enduml
